{"title":"EDU FM Drum — Board 2 (Trigger + VCA + XOR + HPF)","source":"docs/fm_drum_netlist.md","board":"n8synth 10HP","revision":"0.1","notes":"Board 2: DA2 (TL072, rotated 180deg) with gate-to-trigger comparator, accent CV, decay envelope, VCA, XOR pulse gate, Sallen-Key HPF, sine/pulse + FM switches, tune CV. Inter-board from Board 1: SINE_OUT, CAR_SQ, MOD_SQ, UNACC_TRIG (if needed), ACC_TRIG path.","_challenges":["DA2 is 8-pin DIP rotated 180deg. VCA (section B) on left pins 5-7, comparator (section A) on right pins 1-3.","R3 (100K VCC to pin 2) needs +12V routed to right side of board — jumper from row 7L across gap.","Q5 (VCA NPN) collector must reach DA2 pin 6 (row 5L) — long jumper from row 28 area.","XOR gate (4 diodes + PNP) at rows 17-19: CAR_SQ and MOD_SQ arrive at row 1L, need jumpers down.","Decay envelope (row 14L) driven by ACC_TRIG (row 12R) — needs cross-board jumper L to R.","Tune CV PNP pair (Q12/Q13) share base node but connect to separate pot JPS — route carefully.","SINE_OUT arrives from Board 1 at row 1 and must reach switch path at row 26 — long jumper."],"stages":[{"id":1,"name":"ICs + Power","desc":"Install DA2 (TL072 rotated 180deg) and decoupling caps.","test":"Verify +12V on DA2 pin 8 (row 7L), -12V on pin 4 (row 4R).","color":"#888"},{"id":2,"name":"Gate-to-Trigger","desc":"HP filter (C1/R1) + comparator (DA2-A) converts sustained gate to short trigger pulse.","test":"Inject gate at row 1R. Probe COMP_OUT (row 7R) for sharp trigger pulse.","color":"#e74c3c"},{"id":3,"name":"Accent CV","desc":"PNP limiter (Q9) + NPN buffer (Q8) create amplitude-limited ACC_TRIG and full UNACC_TRIG.","test":"ACC_TRIG amplitude varies with accent CV jack voltage.","color":"#c0392b"},{"id":4,"name":"Decay Envelope","desc":"Diode charges C3 (1uF) from ACC_TRIG. Pot + R7 control discharge rate.","test":"Exponential decay on DECAY_CAP (row 14L) after each trigger.","color":"#f39c12"},{"id":5,"name":"Decay CV","desc":"PNP (Q11) sets voltage floor on decay cap. 470K bypass for gradual full discharge.","test":"Higher decay CV = shorter effective decay time.","color":"#e67e22"},{"id":6,"name":"XOR Pulse Gate","desc":"Discrete XOR from 4 diodes + PNP (Q10). Carrier + modulator squares produce ring-mod pulse.","test":"Metallic/chaotic pulse at XOR_OUT (row 19L).","color":"#9b59b6"},{"id":7,"name":"High Pass Filter","desc":"Sallen-Key HPF with NPN follower (Q7). ~7.5kHz cutoff for cymbal/hat sounds.","test":"Only high frequencies at HPF_OUT (row 25L). Low freqs attenuated.","color":"#8e44ad"},{"id":8,"name":"Sine/Pulse Switch","desc":"SW2 (SPDT on control deck) selects sine or HPF pulse as VCA input. R37 scales pulse level.","test":"SW2 toggles between warm sine and harsh pulse character.","color":"#2ecc71"},{"id":9,"name":"VCA + Output","desc":"NPN (Q5) as voltage-controlled fake resistor at DA2-B inverting input. 2M trimmer (RV1) nulls DC offset.","test":"Drum sound at OUTPUT jack. Trim RV1 for zero DC at idle.","color":"#3498db"},{"id":10,"name":"FM Switch","desc":"SW1 (SPDT on control deck) routes modulator triangle or GND to carrier CV mixer on Board 1.","test":"SW1 ON: FM modulation audible. OFF: pure tone.","color":"#27ae60"},{"id":11,"name":"Tune CV","desc":"External CV via PNP pair (Q12/Q13) shifts both tune pot grounds simultaneously.","test":"Tune CV jack changes carrier + modulator pitch together.","color":"#1abc9c"}],"ics":[{"id":"DA2","type":"TL072","topRow":4,"leftCol":"d","rightCol":"g","pins":8,"rotated":true,"stage":1,"_note":"Rotated 180deg. Left col d: pin5(row4)=IN_B+, pin6(row5)=IN_B-, pin7(row6)=OUT_B, pin8(row7)=VCC. Right col g: pin4(row4)=VEE, pin3(row5)=IN_A+, pin2(row6)=IN_A-, pin1(row7)=OUT_A."}],"twoPins":[{"id":"C11","type":"C","value":"100nF","r1":7,"c1":"c","r2":8,"c2":"c","stage":1,"_note":"DA2 VCC decoupling. Pin 8 (row 7L) to adjacent row. Wire row 8 col c to GND."},{"id":"C12","type":"C","value":"100nF","r1":4,"c1":"h","r2":3,"c2":"h","stage":1,"_note":"DA2 VEE decoupling. Pin 4 (row 4R) to row 3R (GND bus)."},{"id":"C14","type":"C","value":"47uF","r1":2,"c1":"b","r2":2,"c2":"c","stage":1,"_note":"Bulk -12V bypass. Electrolytic. Connect to pwrR even row for -12V."},{"id":"C1","type":"C","value":"10nF","r1":1,"c1":"h","r2":2,"c2":"h","stage":2,"_note":"GATE_IN (row 1R) to HP_OUT (row 2R). HP coupling cap."},{"id":"R1","type":"R","value":"39K","r1":2,"c1":"i","r2":3,"c2":"i","stage":2,"_note":"HP_OUT (row 2R) to GND bus (row 3R). HP discharge."},{"id":"R4","type":"R","value":"10K","r1":2,"c1":"j","r2":5,"c2":"j","stage":2,"_note":"HP_OUT (row 2R) to DA2 pin 3 (row 5R). Signal input to comparator (+)."},{"id":"R2","type":"R","value":"5K6","r1":5,"c1":"f","r2":3,"c2":"f","stage":2,"_note":"DA2 pin 3 (row 5R) to GND bus (row 3R). Threshold reference divider bottom."},{"id":"R3","type":"R","value":"100K","r1":9,"c1":"h","r2":6,"c2":"h","stage":2,"_note":"VCC (row 9R via JW1 jumper) to DA2 pin 2 (row 6R). Threshold top."},{"id":"R5","type":"R","value":"33K","r1":7,"c1":"h","r2":5,"c2":"i","stage":2,"_note":"COMP_OUT (pin 1, row 7R) to DA2 pin 3 (row 5R). Positive feedback for hysteresis."},{"id":"R6","type":"R","value":"100K","r1":7,"c1":"j","r2":10,"c2":"j","stage":3,"_note":"COMP_OUT (pin 1, row 7R) to ACC_NODE (row 10R). Also tap UNACC_TRIG from row 7R."},{"id":"D1","type":"D","value":"1N4148","r1":13,"c1":"a","r2":14,"c2":"a","stage":4,"_note":"ACC_TRIG bus (row 13L, anode) to DECAY_CAP (row 14L, cathode). Charge diode."},{"id":"C3","type":"C","value":"1uF","r1":14,"c1":"b","r2":15,"c2":"b","stage":4,"_note":"DECAY_CAP (row 14L) to GND (row 15 odd). Electrolytic, +leg row 14."},{"id":"R7","type":"R","value":"4K7","r1":14,"c1":"c","r2":16,"c2":"c","stage":4,"_note":"DECAY_CAP to GND via POT2 path. Min discharge. Row 16 connects to decay pot JPS."},{"id":"R50","type":"R","value":"470K","r1":14,"c1":"d","r2":15,"c2":"d","stage":5,"_note":"DECAY_CAP (row 14L) to GND (row 15 odd). Slow bypass discharge past CV floor."},{"id":"D9","type":"D","value":"1N4148","r1":17,"c1":"a","r2":18,"c2":"a","stage":6,"_note":"CAR_SQ (row 17L via jumper from row 1, anode) to Q10 emitter node (row 18L, cathode)."},{"id":"D10","type":"D","value":"1N4148","r1":19,"c1":"a","r2":17,"c2":"b","stage":6,"_note":"Q10 base node (row 19L, anode) to CAR_SQ node (row 17L, cathode). Cross-connected."},{"id":"D11","type":"D","value":"1N4148","r1":18,"c1":"b","r2":17,"c2":"c","stage":6,"_note":"Q10 emitter node (row 18L, anode) to MOD_SQ node (row 17R-side via jumper, cathode). See JW3."},{"id":"D12","type":"D","value":"1N4148","r1":17,"c1":"d","r2":19,"c2":"d","stage":6,"_note":"MOD_SQ node (row 17L, anode) to Q10 base node (row 19L, cathode)."},{"id":"R43","type":"R","value":"100K","r1":18,"c1":"c","r2":19,"c2":"c","stage":6,"_note":"Q10 emitter (row 18) to Q10 base (row 19). Bias resistor."},{"id":"R45","type":"R","value":"10K","r1":20,"c1":"a","r2":21,"c2":"a","stage":6,"_note":"XOR_OUT (row 20L from Q10.C) to GND (row 21 odd). Output pull-down."},{"id":"C7","type":"C","value":"470pF","r1":20,"c1":"b","r2":22,"c2":"b","stage":7,"_note":"XOR_OUT (row 20L) to HPF_NODE_A (row 22L). HPF input cap 1."},{"id":"C15","type":"C","value":"470pF","r1":22,"c1":"c","r2":23,"c2":"c","stage":7,"_note":"HPF_NODE_A (row 22L) to Q7 base (row 23L). HPF cap 2."},{"id":"R44","type":"R","value":"100K","r1":22,"c1":"d","r2":24,"c2":"d","stage":7,"_note":"HPF_NODE_A (row 22L) to Q7 emitter (row 24L). Sallen-Key feedback path."},{"id":"R46","type":"R","value":"10K","r1":24,"c1":"b","r2":25,"c2":"b","stage":7,"_note":"HPF_EMIT (row 24L) to VEE_BIAS midpoint (row 25L). Emitter bias 1."},{"id":"R47","type":"R","value":"10K","r1":25,"c1":"a","r2":26,"c2":"a","stage":7,"_note":"VEE_BIAS midpoint (row 25L) to VEE (row 26L). Emitter bias 2."},{"id":"C8","type":"C","value":"15nF","r1":24,"c1":"e","r2":27,"c2":"e","stage":7,"_note":"HPF_EMIT (row 24L) to HPF_OUT (row 27L). DC-blocking output cap."},{"id":"R37","type":"R","value":"18K","r1":27,"c1":"d","r2":28,"c2":"d","stage":8,"_note":"HPF_OUT (row 27L) to SW2 pulse terminal (row 28 JPS). Pulse input scaling."},{"id":"R40","type":"R","value":"47","r1":28,"c1":"e","r2":29,"c2":"e","stage":9,"_note":"TYPE_SW_COM (row 28L from switch JPS) to VCA_BASE_NODE (row 29L). Coupling to Q5 base."},{"id":"R41","type":"R","value":"470K","r1":30,"c1":"a","r2":31,"c2":"a","stage":9,"_note":"Q5 emitter (row 30L) to GND (row 31 odd). VCA emitter bias."},{"id":"R39","type":"R","value":"200K","r1":6,"c1":"a","r2":5,"c2":"a","stage":9,"_note":"VCA_OUT (DA2 pin 7, row 6L) to VCA_INV (DA2 pin 6, row 5L). Feedback resistor."},{"id":"RV1","type":"TRIM","value":"2M","r1":5,"c1":"b","r2":32,"c2":"b","stage":9,"_note":"VCA_INV (pin 6, row 5L) to RV1 wiper (row 32L). DC offset trim. Long span to trimmer."},{"id":"R42","type":"R","value":"1M","r1":32,"c1":"a","r2":33,"c2":"a","stage":9,"_note":"RV1 wiper (row 32L) to GND (row 33 odd). Trim baseline resistor."},{"id":"R48","type":"R","value":"330K","r1":34,"c1":"h","r2":35,"c2":"h","stage":11,"_note":"TUNE_CV_IN (row 34R from J4 JPS) to TUNE_CV_ATT node (row 35R). Input attenuator."},{"id":"R49","type":"R","value":"100K","r1":34,"c1":"i","r2":35,"c2":"i","stage":11,"_note":"POT6 wiper (row 34R JPS) to TUNE_CV_ATT (row 35R). Tune CV INT pot mixing."},{"id":"D13","type":"D","value":"1N4148","r1":35,"c1":"j","r2":36,"c2":"j","stage":11,"_note":"TUNE_CV_BIAS (row 35R, anode) to PNP_BASES (row 36R, cathode). Vbe compensation diode."},{"id":"R52","type":"R","value":"1M","r1":35,"c1":"f","r2":36,"c2":"f","stage":11,"_note":"TUNE_CV_BIAS (row 35R) to VEE path. Ensures current through D13 for consistent Vbe drop."}],"transistors":[{"id":"Q9","type":"PNP","subtype":"BC558","eR":10,"eC":"h","bR":10,"bC":"f","cR":10,"cC":"g","stage":3,"_note":"Accent limiter. E=ACC_NODE (row 10R, same row as R6), B=ACCENT_CV_IN (row 10 col f, from J2 JPS), C=GND (needs wire to pwrR or pwrL GND)."},{"id":"Q8","type":"NPN","subtype":"BC548","eR":12,"eC":"h","bR":11,"bC":"h","cR":11,"cC":"j","stage":3,"_note":"Trigger buffer. E=ACC_TRIG output (row 12R), B=ACC_NODE (row 11R, jumper from row 10), C=VCC (row 11 col j, needs +12V wire)."},{"id":"Q11","type":"PNP","subtype":"BC558","eR":14,"eC":"h","bR":14,"bC":"i","cR":14,"cC":"j","stage":5,"_note":"Decay CV floor. E=DECAY_CAP (row 14, jumper from left side), B=DECAY_CV_IN (from J3 JPS), C=GND (wire to pwrR)."},{"id":"Q10","type":"PNP","subtype":"BC558","eR":18,"eC":"d","bR":19,"bC":"b","cR":20,"cC":"d","stage":6,"_note":"XOR gate PNP. E=diode junction (row 18L), B=diode junction (row 19L), C=XOR_OUT (row 20L). Vertical orientation spanning 3 rows."},{"id":"Q7","type":"NPN","subtype":"BC548","eR":24,"eC":"c","bR":23,"bC":"d","cR":23,"cC":"a","stage":7,"_note":"HPF emitter follower. E=HPF_EMIT (row 24L), B=from C15 (row 23L), C=VCC (row 23 col a, needs +12V wire)."},{"id":"Q5","type":"NPN","subtype":"BC548","eR":30,"eC":"d","bR":29,"bC":"d","cR":30,"cC":"b","stage":9,"_note":"VCA NPN. B=VCA_BASE_NODE (row 29L from R40), C=VCA_INV (needs long jumper to DA2 pin 6 row 5L), E=VCA_EMIT (row 30L to R41)."},{"id":"Q12","type":"PNP","subtype":"BC558","eR":36,"eC":"a","bR":36,"bC":"b","cR":36,"cC":"c","stage":11,"_note":"Tune CV carrier PNP. E=CARRIER_TUNE_BOT (connects to POT4 bottom via inter-board), B=PNP_BASES (from D13 row 36R via jumper), C=GND."},{"id":"Q13","type":"PNP","subtype":"BC558","eR":36,"eC":"h","bR":36,"bC":"i","cR":36,"cC":"j","stage":11,"_note":"Tune CV modulator PNP. E=MOD_TUNE_BOT (connects to POT5 bottom via inter-board), B=PNP_BASES (shared with Q12), C=GND."}],"jumpers":[{"id":"JW1","r1":7,"c1":"e","r2":9,"c2":"f","stage":2,"label":"VCC to right side","_note":"Bring +12V from DA2 VCC (pin 8, row 7L) across to row 9R for R3 threshold."},{"id":"JW2","r1":10,"c1":"f","r2":11,"c2":"f","stage":3,"label":"ACC_NODE to Q8.B","_note":"ACC_NODE (row 10R) to Q8 base area (row 11R)."},{"id":"JW3","r1":12,"c1":"h","r2":13,"c2":"e","stage":3,"label":"ACC_TRIG to decay","_note":"ACC_TRIG (Q8 emitter row 12R) to decay charge bus (row 13L). Cross sides."},{"id":"JW4","r1":1,"c1":"a","r2":17,"c2":"e","stage":6,"label":"CAR_SQ to XOR","_note":"Carrier square from inter-board (row 1L) down to XOR area (row 17). Long jumper wire."},{"id":"JW5","r1":2,"c1":"a","r2":17,"c2":"c","stage":6,"label":"MOD_SQ to XOR","_note":"Modulator square from inter-board (row 2L) down to XOR area (row 17). Long jumper wire."},{"id":"JW6","r1":30,"c1":"b","r2":5,"c2":"c","stage":9,"label":"Q5.C to VCA_INV","_note":"Q5 collector (row 30L) to DA2 pin 6 (row 5L). Long jumper — essential VCA connection."},{"id":"JW7","r1":1,"c1":"e","r2":28,"c2":"a","stage":8,"label":"SINE_OUT to switch","_note":"SINE_OUT from inter-board (row 1L col e) to sine/pulse switch area (row 28L). Long jumper."},{"id":"JW8","r1":14,"c1":"e","r2":14,"c2":"f","stage":5,"label":"DECAY_CAP L to R","_note":"Bridge DECAY_CAP from left side (row 14L) to right side (row 14R) for Q11.E connection."},{"id":"JW9","r1":7,"c1":"i","r2":13,"c2":"d","stage":3,"label":"UNACC_TRIG out","_note":"UNACC_TRIG (COMP_OUT, row 7R) to trigger bus (row 13L). Routes to Board 1 for VCO resets + click."},{"id":"JW10","r1":36,"c1":"d","r2":36,"c2":"g","stage":11,"label":"PNP bases bridge","_note":"Bridge Q12 base (row 36L col b) to Q13 base (row 36R col i) via D13 output. Shared base node."},{"id":"JW11","r1":6,"c1":"e","r2":6,"c2":"f","stage":9,"label":"VCA_OUT bridge","_note":"VCA_OUT (DA2 pin 7, row 6L) across center gap to right side for output routing."},{"id":"JW12","r1":6,"c1":"j","r2":34,"c2":"a","stage":9,"label":"VCA_OUT to output","_note":"VCA_OUT from row 6R to output area (row 34L) for J5 OUTPUT jack JPS."}],"powerWires":[{"r1":7,"c1":"a","r2":8,"c2":"pwrL","label":"DA2 VCC","stage":1,"_note":"Pin 8 (VCC, row 7L) to pwrL row 8 (even=+12V)"},{"r1":4,"c1":"j","r2":4,"c2":"pwrR","label":"DA2 VEE","stage":1,"_note":"Pin 4 (VEE, row 4R) to pwrR row 4 (even=-12V)"},{"r1":3,"c1":"a","r2":3,"c2":"pwrL","label":"GND bus L","stage":1,"_note":"Row 3 left GND bus to pwrL row 3 (odd=GND)"},{"r1":3,"c1":"j","r2":3,"c2":"pwrR","label":"GND bus R","stage":1,"_note":"Row 3 right GND bus to pwrR row 3 (odd=GND)"},{"r1":8,"c1":"c","r2":9,"c2":"pwrL","label":"C11 GND","stage":1,"_note":"C11 far end (row 8L) to GND (pwrL row 9, odd=GND)"},{"r1":15,"c1":"b","r2":15,"c2":"pwrL","label":"C3 GND","stage":4,"_note":"C3 GND leg (row 15L) to pwrL row 15 (odd=GND)"},{"r1":15,"c1":"d","r2":15,"c2":"pwrL","label":"R50 GND","stage":5,"_note":"R50 bypass GND end (row 15L) to pwrL row 15 (odd=GND). Shares GND row with C3."},{"r1":21,"c1":"a","r2":21,"c2":"pwrL","label":"XOR pulldown GND","stage":6,"_note":"R45 GND end (row 21L) to pwrL row 21 (odd=GND)"},{"r1":23,"c1":"a","r2":22,"c2":"pwrL","label":"Q7.C VCC","stage":7,"_note":"Q7 collector (row 23L col a) to +12V. pwrL row 22 (even=+12V)."},{"r1":26,"c1":"a","r2":26,"c2":"pwrR","label":"HPF bias VEE","stage":7,"_note":"R47 VEE end (row 26L) to pwrR row 26 (even=-12V). Emitter bias chain bottom."},{"r1":31,"c1":"a","r2":31,"c2":"pwrL","label":"R41 GND","stage":9,"_note":"R41 GND end (row 31L) to pwrL row 31 (odd=GND)"},{"r1":33,"c1":"a","r2":33,"c2":"pwrL","label":"R42 GND","stage":9,"_note":"R42 trim baseline GND (row 33L) to pwrL row 33 (odd=GND)"},{"r1":4,"c1":"b","r2":5,"c2":"pwrL","label":"DA2 pin5 GND","stage":9,"_note":"DA2 pin 5 IN_B+ (row 4L) to GND (pwrL row 5, odd=GND). VCA non-inv reference."},{"r1":11,"c1":"j","r2":12,"c2":"pwrL","label":"Q8.C VCC","stage":3,"_note":"Q8 collector (row 11R col j) to +12V. Route via jumper/wire to pwrL row 12 (even=+12V)."},{"r1":36,"c1":"c","r2":35,"c2":"pwrL","label":"Q12.C GND","stage":11,"_note":"Q12 collector (row 36L) to GND (pwrL row 35, odd=GND)"},{"r1":36,"c1":"j","r2":35,"c2":"pwrR","label":"Q13.C GND","stage":11,"_note":"Q13 collector (row 36R) to GND (pwrR row 35, odd=GND)"},{"r1":36,"c1":"f","r2":36,"c2":"pwrR","label":"R52 VEE","stage":11,"_note":"R52 VEE end (row 36R) to pwrR row 36 (even=-12V)"}],"jpsWires":[{"id":"J1","col":"j","row":1,"label":"GATE IN jack","stage":2},{"id":"J2","col":"f","row":10,"label":"ACCENT CV jack","stage":3},{"id":"POT2.1","col":"e","row":14,"label":"DECAY pot pin1 (to DECAY_CAP)","stage":4},{"id":"POT2.w","col":"e","row":16,"label":"DECAY pot wiper+pin3","stage":4},{"id":"J3","col":"i","row":14,"label":"DECAY CV jack","stage":5},{"id":"SW2.1","col":"b","row":28,"label":"SINE/PULSE SW term1 (sine path)","stage":8},{"id":"SW2.c","col":"c","row":28,"label":"SINE/PULSE SW common (TYPE_SW_COM)","stage":8},{"id":"SW2.2","col":"d","row":28,"label":"SINE/PULSE SW term2 (pulse via R37)","stage":8},{"id":"SW1.1","col":"h","row":1,"label":"FM SW term1 (MOD_TRI from Board 1)","stage":10},{"id":"SW1.c","col":"i","row":1,"label":"FM SW common (FM_SW_COM to Board 1)","stage":10},{"id":"SW1.g","col":"j","row":3,"label":"FM SW term2 (GND)","stage":10},{"id":"POT6.w","col":"i","row":34,"label":"TUNE CV INT pot wiper","stage":11},{"id":"J4","col":"h","row":34,"label":"TUNE CV jack","stage":11},{"id":"J5","col":"a","row":34,"label":"OUTPUT jack","stage":9}],"netLabels":[{"r":1,"side":"L","name":"CAR_SQ in","stage":6},{"r":1,"side":"R","name":"GATE_IN","stage":2},{"r":2,"side":"L","name":"MOD_SQ in","stage":6},{"r":2,"side":"R","name":"HP_OUT","stage":2},{"r":5,"side":"R","name":"COMP (+)","stage":2},{"r":6,"side":"R","name":"COMP (-)","stage":2},{"r":7,"side":"R","name":"COMP_OUT","stage":2},{"r":4,"side":"L","name":"VCA (+) GND","stage":9},{"r":5,"side":"L","name":"VCA_INV (-)","stage":9},{"r":6,"side":"L","name":"VCA_OUT","stage":9},{"r":10,"side":"R","name":"ACC_NODE","stage":3},{"r":12,"side":"R","name":"ACC_TRIG","stage":3},{"r":13,"side":"L","name":"TRIG bus","stage":3},{"r":14,"side":"L","name":"DECAY_CAP","stage":4},{"r":17,"side":"L","name":"XOR inputs","stage":6},{"r":20,"side":"L","name":"XOR_OUT","stage":6},{"r":22,"side":"L","name":"HPF_NODE_A","stage":7},{"r":24,"side":"L","name":"HPF_EMIT","stage":7},{"r":27,"side":"L","name":"HPF_OUT","stage":7},{"r":28,"side":"L","name":"TYPE_SW_COM","stage":8},{"r":29,"side":"L","name":"VCA_BASE","stage":9},{"r":34,"side":"L","name":"OUTPUT_J","stage":9},{"r":35,"side":"R","name":"TUNE_CV_ATT","stage":11},{"r":36,"side":"L","name":"CAR_TUNE_BOT","stage":11},{"r":36,"side":"R","name":"MOD_TUNE_BOT","stage":11}]}
